verbose_text: The specific miRNA-29c mimics, miRNA-29c inhibitors or scramble miRNA were transiently transfected into U343 cells for 24 h, followed by treatment with parecoxib for another 24 h. RT-qPCR analysis showed that the expression of miRNA-29c was significantly increased and reduced after transfection of miRNA-29c mimics and inhibitors, respectively, in comparison with scramble miRNA (XREF_FIG A).
